snippet.title: Anthem Official Teaser Trailer (2017)
snippet.description:
See more of Anthem at EA Play on June 9th: https://youtu.be/qw16v3oGXso

In Anthem™, a new game from EA's BioWare studio, explore a landscape of primeval beauty, confront the dangers you find, and grow in power with every step.   

Subscribe and be among the first to experience the global Anthem gameplay reveal: http://bit.ly/2qZN5QV   

Tune in to the Xbox E3 Briefing to see the live Gameplay reveal: http://www.xbox.com.

Discover more: http://x.ea.com/32090
